<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">

<style>
  /* Responsive fixes */
  .about-nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
    z-index: 100;
    background: white;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .about-nav {
      position: static;
      top: auto;
      background: transparent;
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .about-nav .list-group-item {
      border: none !important;
      background: #f8f9fa !important;
      border-radius: 12px !important;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  }

  /* Fully responsive timeline */
  .timeline-container {
    position: relative;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }
  .timeline-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #00a7e1, #005eb8);
    border-radius: 3px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-line { left: 30px; }
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .timeline-dot {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: white;
    border: 6px solid;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-dot {
      left: 0;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
  }

  .timeline-content {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 80px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-content {
      padding-left: 80px;
      padding-right: 20px;
    }
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
</style>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero text-white text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,94,184,0.92),rgba(0,94,184,0.95)),url('/img/about-master-hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; min-height:70vh;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-3">About Make-A-Wish</h1>
      <p class="lead fs-4">Tens of thousands of volunteers, donors and supporters help us grant the wish of every child diagnosed with a critical illness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">

        <!-- RESPONSIVE NAVIGATION -->
        <div class="col-lg-3 about-nav mb-4 mb-lg-0">
          <div class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <a href="#mission"     class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Our Mission</a>
            <a href="#history"     class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Our History</a>
            <a href="#timeline"    class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Timeline</a>
            <a href="#structure"   class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Local & Global Structure</a>
            <a href="#funds"       class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Managing Our Funds</a>
            <a href="#leadership"  class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Leadership</a>
            <a href="#careers"     class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Careers</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="col-lg-9">

          <!-- OUR MISSION -->
          <div id="mission" class="mb-5 pb-5 border-bottom">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="fs-4 lead">We grant the wish of every child diagnosed with a critical illness. In the U.S. and its territories, a wish is granted every 34 minutes.</p>
            <p class="fs-5">A wish can be that spark that helps these brave children believe anything is possible — and gives them the strength to fight harder. This one belief guides everything we do.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- OUR HISTORY -->
          <div id="history" class="mb-5 pb-5 border-bottom">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">Our History</h2>
            <p class="fs-5 mb-4">For children diagnosed with critical illnesses, a wish come true can be a crucial turning point. This impact is why we are driven to make every eligible child’s wish come true.</p>

            <div class="row align-items-center g-5 mb-5">
              <div class="col-md-6 order-2 order-md-1">
                <h3>1980 – Chris Greicius</h3>
                <p>Make-A-Wish traces its inspiration to Christopher James Greicius, a 7-year-old boy battling leukemia who wished to be a police officer. In 1980, his Phoenix community made it happen. Chris passed away just days later, but his wish created a movement that has transformed millions of lives.</p>
                <blockquote class="fst-italic text-muted border-start border-primary border-5 ps-4 mt-4">
                  “He was only seven years, 269 days old when he died. But he taught me about being a man, even though he was only a boy.”<br>
                  <small>— Tommy Austin, Make-A-Wish co-founder</small>
                </blockquote>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 order-1 order-md-2 text-center">
                <img src="/img/chris-greicius.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow w-100" alt="Chris Greicius">
              </div>
            </div>

            <h4 class="mt-5">1981 – The First Official Wish: Bopsy Salazar</h4>
            <p>Frank “Bopsy” Salazar, age 7, became the first official Make-A-Wish child. The Phoenix and Anaheim Fire Departments made him a firefighter and took his family to Disneyland — the very first Disney wish.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- TIMELINE – FULLY RESPONSIVE -->
          <div id="timeline" class="mb-5 pb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold text-center mb-5 display-5">Our Journey of Hope</h2>
            <div class="timeline-container">
              <div class="timeline-line"></div>

              <!-- 1980 -->
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot border-primary"><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-primary fs-3"></i></div>
                <div class="timeline-content text-lg-end text-start" style="margin-left:50%;">
                  <div class="timeline-year bg-primary text-white">1980</div>
                  <h4>Chris Greicius’ Wish</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">A 7-year-old boy’s dream to be a police officer sparked a global movement.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 1981 -->
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot border-danger"><i class="bi bi-heart-fill text-danger fs-3"></i></div>
                <div class="timeline-content text-lg-start" style="margin-right:50%;">
                  <div class="timeline-year bg-danger text-white">1981</div>
                  <h4>First Official Wish</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">Frank “Bopsy” Salazar becomes the first official wish kid.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 1983 -->
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot border-success"><i class="bi bi-building text-success fs-3"></i></div>
                <div class="timeline-content text-lg-end text-start" style="margin-left:50%;">
                  <div class="timeline-year bg-success text-white">1983</div>
                  <h4>Official Incorporation</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">Make-A-Wish Foundation of America is officially born.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 1993 -->
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot border-warning"><i class="bi bi-globe text-warning fs-3"></i></div>
                <div class="timeline-content text-lg-start" style="margin-right:50%;">
                  <div class="timeline-year bg-warning text-dark">1993</div>
                  <h4>Going Global</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">Make-A-Wish International is formed — now serving 50 countries.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 2020 -->
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot border-info"><i class="bi bi-cake2-fill text-info fs-3"></i></div>
                <div class="timeline-content text-lg-end text-start" style="margin-left:50%;">
                  <div class="timeline-year bg-info text-white">2020</div>
                  <h4>40 Years of Wishes</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">Over 500,000 wishes granted worldwide.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 2025 & Beyond -->
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot border-primary" style="width:80px;height:80px;"><i class="bi bi-stars text-primary fs-1"></i></div>
                <div class="timeline-content text-lg-start" style="margin-right:50%;">
                  <div class="timeline-year bg-primary text-white fs-4">2025 & Beyond</div>
                  <h4>The Journey Continues</h4>
                  <p class="fw-bold">With supporters like YOU, we’re granting more wishes than ever.</p>
                  <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-wish mt-3">Be Part of Our Future</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- LOCAL & GLOBAL STRUCTURE -->
          <div id="structure" class="mb-5 pb-5 border-bottom">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">Local & Global Structure</h2>
            <p>Make-A-Wish is one united family — but also a collection of independently chartered nonprofit organizations sharing the same vision.</p>
            <ul class="fs-5">
              <li><strong>Make-A-Wish America</strong> – National office in Phoenix sets standards and raises national funds</li>
              <li><strong>Local Chapters</strong> – Independent chapters with their own boards bring wishes to life in every community</li>
              <li><strong>Make-A-Wish International</strong> – Serves 50 countries on 6 continents through 40 affiliates</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">Together we have granted more than <strong>585,000 wishes worldwide</strong> — making us the world’s largest wish-granting organization.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- MANAGING OUR FUNDS -->
          <div id="funds" class="mb-5 pb-5 border-bottom">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">Managing Our Funds</h2>
            <div class="row text-center g-4">
              <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <h1 class="text-success fw-bold display-4">86¢</h1>
                <p class="fs-5">of every dollar goes directly to granting wishes</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <h1 class="text-info fw-bold display-4">4-Star</h1>
                <p class="fs-5">Charity Navigator rating for 15+ years</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <h1 class="text-warning fw-bold display-4">Platinum</h1>
                <p class="fs-5">GuideStar/Candid Seal of Transparency</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- LEADERSHIP -->
          <div id="leadership" class="mb-5 pb-5 border-bottom">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-5">Leadership</h2>
            <div class="row g-4">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow">
                  <img src="/img/R. Dominksi.jpg" class="card-img-top" style="height:220px; object-fit:cover;" alt="Sarah Johnson">
                  <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5>Sarah Johnson</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted">President & CEO</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow">
                  <img src="/img/PCC.png" class="card-img-top" style="height:220px; object-fit:cover;" alt="Michael Chen">
                  <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5>Michael Chen</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted">Chief Operating Officer</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow">
                  <img src="/img/_M0I7226.jpg" class="card-img-top" style="height:220px; object-fit:cover;" alt="Emma Rodriguez">
                  <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5>Emma Rodriguez</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted">VP of Wish Granting</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- CAREERS -->
          <div id="careers" class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">Careers at Make-A-Wish</h2>
            <p class="fs-5">Want to help create life-changing wishes every day? Join our passionate team!</p>
            <a href="mailto:careers@Make-A-Wish.org" class="btn btn-wish btn-lg">View Open Positions</a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script>
    // Smooth scroll + active menu highlight
    document.querySelectorAll('.about-nav a').forEach(link => {
      link.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
        window.scrollTo({ top: target.offsetTop - 100, behavior: 'smooth' });
      });
    });

    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      let current = '';
      document.querySelectorAll('div[id]').forEach(section => {
        if (window.scrollY >= section.offsetTop - 150) {
          current = section.getAttribute('id');
        }
      });
      document.querySelectorAll('.about-nav a').forEach(a => {
        a.classList.remove('active');
        if (a.getAttribute('href') === `#${current}`) a.classList.add('active');
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>